---
title: Feta Believe It Chicken Shawarma Wraps Elevated Dinners, Impressively Easy
description: This fabulously fast and flavorful wrap is packed with juicy shawarma-seasoned sautéed chicken, salty-savory feta cheese, juicy tomato slices, and wholesome fresh spinach tossed in a garlicky dressing along with a bright squeeze of fresh lemon juice. It’s served with a side of crunchy blue corn tortilla chips and creamy hummus for dipping. You feta believe it—this quick and filling meal will be on your table in just 15 minutes!
